---
title: Grilled Turkey Sammies with Blueberry Mayo
description: Sweet and savoury combine in a one-of-a-kind Canadian sammy! BBQ grilled turkey gets paired with spicy arugula, creamy blueberry mayo and a crisp apple salad for a summery feast.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sandwichs-a-la-dinde-grillee-ab05d41e.jpg
